<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Penbrooke Meadows</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">A part of the International Avenue Business Revitalization Zone, the community is bordered by the 17th Avenue SE on the south, the 52nd Street E on the west, the 68th Street E to the east and the Memorial Drive on the north.</p>
            <p class="par-xl">Although most popular among first time home buyers, Penbrooke Meadows real estate also offers a variety of housing options for investors as well. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Homes for sale in Penbrooke Meadows comprise single-family detached homes, bungalows as well as apartments and condominiums that are regularly available at an average price of $350,000. </p>
        </div>
